{"tid":771991,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"露比蘿絲成為超級英雄！主演DC美劇《蝙蝠女俠》演繹出櫃女主角","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T11:17:48.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"691fb48ce53ccaab0cb258e33314bf49290718e8","tid":771991,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/08/195022_8d5ba13c154947cbaa50fce72672b26b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F195022_8d5ba13c154947cbaa50fce72672b26b.jpg&h=cb491f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCW 先前宣布將開發《蝙蝠女俠》（Batwoman）美劇。時隔半個月後，電視網宣布主演人選，將由《勁爆女子監獄》澳洲女星露比蘿絲（Ruby Rose）擔任，成為真人版超級英雄影集首位同性戀主角。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《蝙蝠女俠》以二代蝙蝠女俠凱特凱恩（Kate Kane）作為主角，為一名出櫃的女同性戀。她擁有對社會正義的熱情使命，以及為自己的理想而暢言的才華。作為一名訓練有素的街頭戰士，她準備好剷除這個淪陷城市中，再次興起的犯罪活動。但還不要稱她為英雄，在一個渴望救世主的城市中，凱特必須先克服自己的心魔，才能接受被喚作高譚的希望象徵。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n該劇由 CW-DC 系列影集製作人葛瑞格貝蘭提（Greg Berlanti）帶領原班人馬打造。《超人前傳(2001)》、《噬血Y世代》編劇卡洛琳德里斯（Caroline Dries）執筆劇本並擔任執行製作。製片公司包括葛瑞格貝蘭提的 Berlanti Productions 、DC 娛樂以及華納兄弟電視公司。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BmL88D0h6Dt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=embed_loading_state_control\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBmL88D0h6Dt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dembed_loading_state_control&d=y8y8TxoB%2BWH7vemxOF3vhYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c4f37461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBmL88D0h6Dt%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dembed_loading_state_control&h=15d09064\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BmL88D0h6Dt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=embed_loading_state_control</a><br />\n露比蘿絲飾演的蝙蝠女俠將於今年底的綠箭宇宙交叉集率先登場。去年一同加入的《明日傳奇》（DC&rsquo;s Legends of Tomorrow）則確定不會在今年的交叉集中現身。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n露比蘿絲因《勁爆女子監獄》一劇走紅後，前進大銀幕演出多部票房電影，包括《惡靈古堡：最終章》、《限制級戰警：重返極限》、《捍衛任務2：殺神回歸》、《歌喉讚3》。最新一部參演電影《巨齒鯊》將於 8 月 10 日在台灣上映。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《蝙蝠女俠》若順利獲得預訂成季，將於 2019 年在 CW 首播。（hollywoodreporter）"},{"pid":"b4994e5061e28cb05882b429af293282cd2bd182","tid":771991,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"痴線,又開多套,近年d超級英雄戲/劇,好似井噴咁,有d厭倦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然咁講對果d只係想睇蝙蝠女的粉絲唔公道,&quot;理得你前面出過幾多套啫,我淨係想睇呢套/會追呢套&quot;"},{"pid":"d140638d7adcb560e4afb2dbf2622ae80bdfb8f2","tid":771991,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"Batwoman等唔等於Batgirl?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3852be5d4bacd7d164654f8b4998b1fa7c4a72","tid":771991,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d140638d7adcb560e4afb2dbf2622ae80bdfb8f2","tid":771991,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"Batwoman等唔等於Batgirl?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"唔一樣"},{"pid":"278d53e0fc86095d9d8ff2ed68e5017bddc37548","tid":771991,"uid":32401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"今次個主打位應該係同性戀，"},{"pid":"cb5ab71ecd98f507508d2cc705a453098946ffa7","tid":771991,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278d53e0fc86095d9d8ff2ed68e5017bddc37548","tid":771991,"uid":32401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"今次個主打位應該係同性戀，"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"CW最鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多元民族 LGBT 女權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ea9b7